title: The Everything Calorie Counting Cookbook by Paula Conway
description:
Calculate Your Daily Caloric Intake--and Fat, Carbs, and Daily Fiber--With These 300 Delicious Recipes

If counting calories makes you cringe, this easy-to-use cookbook is just what you need! Mix and match recipes to effortlessly map out your meals for a day, a week, or a month. Based on a 1,200-calorie-a-day diet, The Everything Calorie Counting Cookbook features 300 mouth-watering recipes for every occasion, from super suppers to sensible snacks, including:
Banana Chocolate Chip Pancake Wrap
Honey and Cheese Stuffed Figs
Creamy Potato Soup
Beef Fondue
Chili-Crusted Sea Scallops
Chicken and Green Bean Casserole
Spicy Ranch Chicken Wrap
Chocolate Chip Peanut Butter Pie
Reward your taste buds while you count calories. You can have it all - and eat it, too!
